{"tid":958775,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"艾兒芬妮主演多倫多影展作品《Teen Spirit》正式預告上線","createTime":"2018-12-28T05:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T10:37:33.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3e65e94bbe972d12dc87cee79a7b968ebd22f1","tid":958775,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://consequenceofsound.files.wordpress.com/2018/09/tiff.jpg?quality=80&amp;w=807\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fconsequenceofsound.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F09%2Ftiff.jpg%3Fquality%3D80%26w%3D807&h=fc8f0c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n艾兒芬妮（Elle Fanning）繼坎城影展競賽片《霓虹惡魔》（The Neon Demon）飾演天生麗質的年輕模特兒之後，今年則在多倫影展特別放映單元中的《Teen Spirit》裡飾演一名追求星夢的少女，日前由 Bleecker Street 釋出了正式完整預告。<br />\n《Teen Spirit》由麥斯明格拉（Max Minghella）及編劇，故事描述一名住在懷特島的害羞青少女夢想成為流行明星並且離開她成長的小鎮與破碎的家庭，而透過一位感覺不太可靠的前輩的幫助下，她參加了一個國際歌唱比賽，這也是測試她的才華與野心的大好機會。<br />\n其他演出卡司還包括蕾貝卡霍爾（Rebecca Hall）、佐拉科布尼瑞克（Zlatko Buric）、阿涅斯卡葛羅哈斯卡（Agnieszka Grochowska）等，而電影當中除了會使用亞莉安娜（Ariana Grande）、艾麗高登（Ellie Goulding）等人的歌曲外，也將會有由艾兒芬妮親自演唱的原創歌曲。<br />\n除此此外，此片也網羅了《樂來越愛你》（La La Land）金獎提名製作人弗萊德伯格（Fred Berger）、參與《樂來越愛你》歌曲創作的馬瑞斯德維瑞斯（Marius De Vries）配樂、《帕羅奧圖年少》（Palo Alto）攝影師奧藤杜洛德（Autumn Durald）掌鏡，2019 年 4 月 5 日美國上映。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CkA6DpQEKTU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCkA6DpQEKTU&d=WObLFkPojlBXhKjzmUFix5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=dd6aa446\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CkA6DpQEKTU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hypesphere.com%2Fnews%2F16215&d=WObLFkPojlBXhKjzmUFix5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=c739ac04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16215</a>"},{"pid":"33dd009124be89d06348c7aadf28aea1cdbfb832","tid":958775,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea80d95b1aa273b269cd9d7afa34f2b00a92273","tid":958775,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cd32c06a1e106d0474c92972a118005d0320b6c","tid":958775,"uid":16092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:31:41.000Z","msg":"佢有份嘅戲唔知點解好多都冇喺香港上畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfeee67ec8bd8915c3bf38523a54dd15443e970c","tid":958775,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5cd32c06a1e106d0474c92972a118005d0320b6c","tid":958775,"uid":16092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:31:41.000Z","msg":"佢有份嘅戲唔知點解好多都冇喺香港上畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"因為佢有份演既戲大部分都唔係商業片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e4c99cdeb872e217224cece5c0606506b73930","tid":958775,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:41:27.000Z","msg":"老婆又有新戲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e390496310a291cc209d1b242377e35d50860ec7","tid":958775,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主</span>老婆又有新戲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e9191d2b78f6f8c2096adb5dec4f25dc9dce92e5","tid":958775,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ea80d95b1aa273b26